'''LowLandLions (LLL/LION)''' was an esports organization currently competing in the Benelux. Founded in 2007, the Dutch organization has held teams in several Esports titles under their brand until their disband in late 2016. In 2020, the team merged with [[Defusekids]] and was re-formed under the Belgian organization's guidance. They are currently operating in partnership with the '''[https://www.kaagent.be/nl KAA Gent]''' football club.

